"title": "1160: God, unchangeableness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1160",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's nature, plans and actions do not change even though he is active and his relationships do not remain static. His moral consistency guarantees his commitment to unchanging principles.</p>\n<h2>God's being is unchangeable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:27\">PSA 102:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:12\">HEB 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:6\">MAL 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:8\">HEB 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's characteristics do not change</h2>\n<h3>God's love is constant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:2\">PSA 89:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:1-Ps136:26\">PSA 136:1–136:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>God's purposes and plans do not change</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:17\">HEB 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:29\">1SA 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:29\">JER 44:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:21\">HEB 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:4\">PSA 110:4</a></p>\n<h2>God does not revoke his promises</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:11\">PSA 132:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:13\">PSA 145:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1\">HEB 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>God's word does not change</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:8\">ISA 40:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:23–1:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's failure to inflict promised judgment is a sign of his unchanging grace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:8\">HOS 11:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:10-Exod32:14\">EXO 32:10–32:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:10\">JON 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a></p>",
